         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">On the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Display</uicontrol> check that the inverter
is supplying the load, and that the bypass is available and within
tolerance.</cmd>
